As an autolisp developer, I want a good autolisp code debugger.

See the specifications in
clautolisp/documentation/clautolisp-debugger-spec.org

Planify and implement the modules of the clautolisp debugger, inspector,
with the dump terminal UI, the ncurses (cl-charms / PDCurses UI), and
the emacs interface (that we'll name aldb as slime debugger is named sldb).


